This project is dual-purpose: it is intended both as a standalone tool and as an
upstream contribution to the Nmap Scripting Engine.

NSE components (offered for upstream contribution)
--------------------------------------------------
The following files are licensed under the same terms as Nmap itself - the Nmap Public
Source License (NPSL), https://nmap.org/npsl/:

    scripts/mcp-info.nse
    scripts/mcp-enum.nse
    scripts/mcp.lua
    scripts/llm-info.nse
    scripts/llm.lua
    nmap-service-probes.mcp
    nmap-service-probes.llm
    nmap-services.llm

Each NSE file carries the standard in-file header:
    license = "Same as Nmap--See https://nmap.org/book/man-legal.html"

